name: 3D Inspired LoRA
description:
This is an experimental LoRA. I merged two of my own LoRA's together, one that was based off of Overwatch Blender art and one that was based off of non-Overwatch Blender art. It was to my surprise that the Overwatch 3D community is way further ahead in terms of quality than the rest of the Blender NSFW community (IMO), so the merge was for qualitative reasons.

I would use this at 1.0 strength to get the full 3D effect. It was trained on NovelAI, so it's best used on Anime models. I used AOM3 for the first four pics, and Hires Fix on for all of them. For the last four pics, I used my custom models Sardonyx and Galena cough cough. This model requires no keywords, but I assume if you put in 'overwatch', it'll mimic the Overwatch style better.

This model tends to generate very voluptuous women, so be warned. You might wanna tone it down in the prompt.

I also have a Discord. Join if you wanna share results, get advice, or make requests.
